featured_reviews.review_id: I'm in the process of launching an e-commerce store. I found Blanka while searching for suppliers. Which I have found it to be extremely difficult to find quality suppliers. Blanka has been so helpful, has a live person to answer to answer every single question via chat!! I haven't had to pick up the phone once and I have my own quality branded products(200+) to upload to my site. I would recommend Blanka to anyone looking for a supplier. Really hard to the level of service Blanka provides anymore.
